                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "once per day, plus overcharge",
                    "effect": "You cast  *oaken resilience* of the indicated rank, and the target sprouts long thorns like those of a hawthorn tree. While  *oaken resilience* lasts, any creature that hits the target with an unarmed Strike or otherwise touches it takes piercing damage from the thorns, with the amount determined by the wand\u2019s type. A creature that has engulfed or swallowed the target takes this damage as well at the start of each of the target\u2019s turns.",
